3. Convert Feet and Inches into Meter and Centimeter
Conversion Formulas:
1\ foot = 0.3048\ meter
1\ inch = 2.54\ centimeter
# Convert feet and inches into meter and centimeter

feet = float(input("Enter feet: "))
inches = float(input("Enter inches: "))

meters = feet * 0.3048
centimeters = inches * 2.54

print("Meters =", meters)
print("Centimeters =", centimeters)
Example Execution
Enter feet: 5
Enter inches: 10

Meters = 1.524
Centimeters = 25.4
