5. Selling Price of Book
Selling Price Formula:
SP = CP - Discount
# Selling price of book

cost_price = float(input("Enter cost price of book: "))
discount = float(input("Enter discount amount: "))

selling_price = cost_price - discount

print("Selling Price =", selling_price)
Example Execution
Enter cost price of book: 500
Enter discount amount: 50

