6. Total Salary of Employee
Salary Formula:
Total\ Salary = Basic + DA + TA + HRA
# Total salary calculation

basic = float(input("Enter basic salary: "))

da = 0.10 * basic
ta = 0.12 * basic
hra = 0.15 * basic

total_salary = basic + da + ta + hra

print("DA =", da)
print("TA =", ta)
print("HRA =", hra)
print("Total Salary =", total_salary)
Example Execution
Enter basic salary: 20000

DA = 2000.0
TA = 2400.0
HRA = 3000.0
Total Salary = 27400.0
