7. Sum of Three-Digit Number
# Sum of three-digit number

num = int(input("Enter a three-digit number: "))

digit1 = num // 100
digit2 = (num // 10) % 10
digit3 = num % 10

sum_digits = digit1 + digit2 + digit3

print("Sum of digits =", sum_digits)
Example Execution
Enter a three-digit number: 456

Sum of digits = 15
